reviewText: I bought this dvd, because I love brazil ladies and I know DJ Vlad is a great DJ, but I was very dissappointed in this DVD. None of the women got completely nude in their teases and the music was terrible and I know DJ Vlad is better than that! I would not recommend this DVD to guys (and/or women) who want to see beautiful brazilian babes mixed with great music, if you want that then get HIP HOP BADGIRLS and HIP HOP HONEYS: BRAZIL BOOM BOOM, those are great DVDs. This DVD boast a beautiful brazil babe named BABALU (who,like most brailian babes in these type of dvds, is a pornstar) and even she didn't get completely nude. The music was horrible compared to the dvds I mentioned, I know DJ Vlad can do better, lets hope so.
